OL,5,FAn ITV News investigation has found
OL,6,Fthat Welsh primary schools are still
OL,7,Fencouraged to teach reading in the
OL,8,Fwrong way.
OL,10,FWhen Lisa's daughter Poppy started
OL,11,Fstruggling with reading, she wasn't
OL,12,Ftoo concerned.
OL,14,FLisa told me her daughter's teachers
OL,15,Fwould say: "Oh she'll pick it up, it
OL,16,Fwill come eventually."
