OL,3,CInside Wales' reading crisis
OL,5,FITV News has analysed hundreds of
OL,6,Fprimary school inspection reports,
OL,7,Fschool websites, and teaching
OL,8,Fresources and found that not only are
OL,9,Fthese methods commonplace in
OL,10,Fclassrooms across Wales, but their use
OL,11,Fis praised by school inspectors.
OL,13,FA small minority of schools and
OL,14,Fparents are taking matters into their
OL,15,Fown hands and ignoring the guidance of
OL,16,Fthe national curriculum, but several
OL,17,Freading experts have shared their
OL,18,Ffears with ITV News that this confused
OL,19,Fapproach to reading instruction is
OL,20,Fdamaging the futures of thousands of
OL,21,FWelsh children.
