OL,5,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,6,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,7,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,8,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,10,FIn the most recent international
OL,11,Feducation tests known as PISA, the
OL,12,Freading scores of Welsh 15-year-olds
OL,13,Fplummeted to their worst-ever level.
OL,14,FThey have been significantly below the
OL,15,Frest of the UK and the international
OL,16,Faverage for decades.
OL,18,FThe poorest children are also falling
OL,19,Ffurther behind their classmates.
