OL,3,CInside Wales' reading crisis
OL,5,FWales' new curriculum continues to
OL,6,Fencourage young children to use
OL,7,Fpictures and context to tackle
OL,8,Funfamiliar words in the initial stages
OL,9,Fof reading. This teaching method is
OL,10,Foften referred to as "cueing".
OL,12,FIt is based on an old, discredited
OL,13,Fassumption that learning to read
OL,14,Fhappens naturally, like learning to
OL,15,Ftalk, and that expert readers don't
OL,16,Fread every letter of a word.
