OL,5,FA method called systematic synthetic
OL,6,Fphonics has been found to be one of
OL,7,Fthe most effective methods of teaching
OL,8,Freading.
OL,10,F"Those that are capable, confident
OL,11,Freaders, you can show them a word that
OL,12,Fis in their vocabulary completely in
OL,13,Fisolation and they'll be able to work
OL,14,Fout what it is," says Christopher
OL,15,FSuch, an experienced teacher and
OL,16,Fauthor of The Art and Science of
OL,17,FTeaching Primary Reading.
