OL,5,FIt has been described by leading
OL,6,Feducational psychologists as "helpful
OL,7,Ffor all children, harmful for none,
OL,8,Fand crucial for some."
OL,10,FEducation systems across the English-
OL,11,Fspeaking world have been turning their
OL,12,Fbacks on cueing. In England, it used
OL,13,Fto be known as the "searchlights"
OL,14,Fmodel. Following a parliamentary
OL,15,Finquiry in 2005, it was abolished,
OL,16,Fwith the UK government mandating the
OL,17,Fteaching of systematic synthetic
OL,18,Fphonics instead.
