OL,3,CInside Wales' reading crisis
OL,5,FSince the abolition of the cueing
OL,6,Fmethod in England and the introduction
OL,7,Fof a phonics screening check, reading
OL,8,Ftest scores in England have risen,
OL,9,Ftaking them to near the top of
OL,10,Finternational rankings.
OL,12,FWhat is being taught in classrooms in
OL,13,FWales?
OL,15,FWhat we've known for decades about how
OL,16,Freading should be taught has still not
OL,17,Freached most Welsh classrooms.
