OL,3,CInside Wales' reading crisis
OL,5,FIn our analysis of primary school
OL,6,Finspection reports, we found more than
OL,7,Fa hundred examples of the schools'
OL,8,Finspectorate, Estyn, praising the use
OL,9,Fof these discredited methods in the
OL,10,Flast five years.
OL,12,FIn one local authority, official
OL,13,F"catch up" reading resources encourage
OL,14,Fteachers to "help the children read
OL,15,Funfamiliar words" by "using picture
OL,16,Fcues".
OL,18,FSchool websites from across Wales are
OL,19,Falso littered with posters encouraging
OL,20,Fparents to use these strategies at
OL,21,Fhome.
