OL,5,F"That is not something that I would
OL,6,Fexpect to read about teaching in a
OL,7,Fschool in the 21st century. We've just
OL,8,Fmoved light years away from that," she
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,FAnother concern of reading researchers
OL,12,Fis that phonics is not being taught
OL,13,Fearly enough in many classrooms. In
OL,14,FWelsh language schools, children do
OL,15,Fnot start learning English literacy
OL,16,Funtil they are six or seven years old.
OL,18,FMixed methods
