OL,3,CInside Wales' reading crisis
OL,5,FThe Welsh government insists its
OL,6,Fcurriculum does include the systematic
OL,7,Fteaching of phonics. This is true. In
OL,8,Ffact, you would struggle to find a
OL,9,Fschool in Wales that doesn't teach
OL,10,Fphonics. But cueing strategies are
OL,11,Fmandated alongside it.
OL,13,FOne headteacher in Cardiff told me
OL,14,Fthat using picture and context cues
OL,15,Fcan cancel out the benefits of
OL,16,Fteaching phonics.
