OL,3,CInside Wales' reading crisis
OL,5,FWe also sent a list of questions to
OL,6,Fher department, but these were not
OL,7,Fanswered specifically.
OL,9,FInstead, a Welsh Government
OL,10,Fspokeswoman said: "Literacy is a top
OL,11,Fpriority within the Curriculum for
OL,12,FWales. We do not advocate any one
OL,13,Fspecific method to teach reading,
OL,14,Frather we enable teachers to use their
OL,15,Fprofessional judgement and knowledge
OL,16,Fof their learners to use the best tool
OL,17,Fto meet the individual needs of their
OL,18,Flearners.
