OL,5,F"The Curriculum for Wales guidance is
OL,6,Fclear that the systematic and
OL,7,Fconsistent teaching of phonics must be
OL,8,Fa key part of the toolkit in our
OL,9,Fschools, alongside vocabulary building
OL,10,Fand comprehension to ensure learners
OL,11,Fare able to understand and make sense
OL,12,Fof what they read and become fluent
OL,13,Fand effective readers.
