OL,5,F"We recognise there is a need to
OL,6,Fimprove reading outcomes for our
OL,7,Flearners. Earlier this year, the
OL,8,FCabinet Secretary for Education set
OL,9,Fout a range of extra support for
OL,10,Fschools including further support for
OL,11,Fliteracy. This support will be based
OL,12,Fupon the latest evidence and co-
OL,13,Fconstructed with experts and
OL,14,Fpractitioners."
